Dejean, 1828]. Type locality: &quot;All[eghen]y, P[ennsylvani]a&quot; (neotype label). Neotype (♂), designated by Lindroth and Freitag (1969: 342), in MCZ [# 32962]. Note. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="«Indiana»">&quot;Indiana&quot;</normalizedToken>
was the area originally cited by Say (1830b: (5) [3]).
</paragraph>
