</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="514" pageNumber="515" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="514" pageNumber="515">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="514" pageNumber="515">
This species ranges from southwestern Pennsylvania (Lindroth and Freitag 1969: 342) to 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“Iowa”">&quot;Iowa&quot;</normalizedToken>
(Jaques and Redlinger 1946: 297), south to east-central Louisiana (West Feliciana Parish, LSAM), northern Alabama (
<normalizedToken originalValue="Löding">Loeding</normalizedToken>
1945: 16; Madison County, CMNH), and northern Georgia (Fattig 1949: 25).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
